body: "## Context\nTracks GH-427. Nightly Validation run 28698219516 (2026-07-04, windows-latest / Node 24): 4 failures, all POSIX-only error-code assertions.\n\n- restore-command.spec: expects code EACCES after chmod 0o444 on the history file; Windows Node 24 raises EPERM opening a read-only file for append.\n- history-rewrite.spec: expects EISDIR writing to a directory path; Windows raises EPERM.\n\n## Approach\nPlatform-tolerant assertions: accept EACCES|EPERM and EISDIR|EPERM respectively (match on a set, not equality). Precedent: PR#365 Windows fixes and the 2026-07-04 GH-427 EPERM fix noted in the ecosystem audit — check whether that partial fix already covers some of the 4 and only patch the remainder. The windows-regression CI job is the oracle; nightly re-run green closes GH-427.\n\n## Definition of done\nAll 4 specs pass on windows-latest Node 24 nightly; no weakening on POSIX (still asserts the specific POSIX code there or the set matcher documents why); GH-427 closed with the green run linked."
